1
00:00:03,440 --> 00:00:05,160
(After being a substitute for so long,)

2
00:00:06,400 --> 00:00:07,440
(will I forget)

3
00:00:09,560 --> 00:00:10,680
(who I truly am?)

4
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:26,960
(They call me He Rufei.)

5
00:00:27,320 --> 00:00:27,880
Kneel.

6
00:00:28,680 --> 00:00:30,200
(The eldest son of the He family.)

7
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:32,720
(Since childhood,)

8
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:34,960
(I was disguised as a boy.)

9
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:36,000
(Visionary Foresight)

10
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,600
(I've always had to wear a mask.)

11
00:00:38,480 --> 00:00:39,320
(They said,)

12
00:00:40,480 --> 00:00:41,040
("live")

13
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:43,140
("without recognition")

14
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:44,800
("and die")

15
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,600
("without a trace.")

16
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:52,800
(I hated it.)

17
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:53,360
Remember.

18
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:55,520
(Yet found solace too.)

19
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:58,560
(This cold mask)

20
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:00,240
(smothered my identity)

21
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,920
(yet forged my purpose.)

22
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,080
(Amidst the smoke of war)

23
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:09,800
(and seas of blood,)

24
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,960
(I forgot life and death)

25
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:14,000
(and stopped wondering)

26
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:15,760
(who I am)

27
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,600
(beneath the mask.)

28
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:22,480
(From a nameless foot soldier,)

29
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,480
(I fought)

30
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:26,400
(to become
the invincible General Feihong.)

31
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,160
(But in the end,)

32
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:34,280
(who is General Feihong?)

33
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:35,960
(Who)

34
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,680
(am I?)

35
00:01:56,850 --> 00:01:59,660
♪Shrugging off past burdens♪

36
00:01:59,660 --> 00:02:02,240
♪Beneath the mask, who am I?♪

37
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:06,320
♪Release and find wider shores♪

38
00:02:08,020 --> 00:02:11,020
♪Love's a riddle, and rain pours heavy♪

39
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,920
♪Crossed paths, now downward fall♪

40
00:02:14,270 --> 00:02:17,700
♪From dust arises starlight's spark♪

41
00:02:19,460 --> 00:02:24,680
♪Tearing through
the night's dense blockade♪

42
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:30,440
♪Heart's flame illuminates all solitude♪

43
00:02:31,230 --> 00:02:33,730
♪Let time's sails drift endlessly♪

44
00:02:33,730 --> 00:02:36,340
♪Through wandering exile♪

45
00:02:36,850 --> 00:02:44,120
♪Breaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew♪

46
00:02:45,090 --> 00:02:47,840
♪Moon as song, life as flame♪

47
00:02:47,900 --> 00:02:50,740
♪Nameless heart clings fiercely♪

48
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,060
♪Let me♪

49
00:02:52,260 --> 00:02:56,340
♪Charge toward the next raging river♪

50
00:02:56,790 --> 00:02:59,470
♪Moon darts, snow falls♪

51
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:02,450
♪We tread rugged paths to reunite♪

52
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:04,090
♪Hands held tight♪

53
00:03:04,090 --> 00:03:08,270
♪We forever live for love's sake♪

54
00:03:08,620 --> 00:03:18,880
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

55
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:26,020
=Legend of The Female General=

56
00:03:26,020 --> 00:03:29,150
=Episode 1=

57
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:31,680
(In the 20th year
of Wei's Qingyuan era,)

58
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,600
(Battlefield of Mingshui)
(Wutuo invaded Wei again.)

59
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:35,880
(Emperor Chengping)

60
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,720
(ordered General Xiao Zhongwu,)

61
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:38,720
(Xiao Army's commander)

62
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,480
(who beat Wutuo five years ago,)

63
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,079
(Xiao Zhongwu, Xiao Army's Commander)
(to march to battle.)

64
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,720
(But at Mingshui's final battle,)

65
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,000
(30,000 Xiao troops)

66
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,880
(fell into an ambush.)

67
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:53,440
Xiao Zhongwu,

68
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:54,920
He Rufei's Fuyue Army

69
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,040
won't be coming.

70
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,560
Surrender,

71
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,240
and we'll spare you.

72
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,720
He Rufei

73
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,040
will come without fail!

74
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:07,120
Wei soldiers

75
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:13,800
choose death over surrender.

76
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:16,959
Charge!

77
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,000
General Xiao!

78
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:40,640
General Xiao!

79
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,920
General Xiao!

80
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:54,920
Father!

81
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:05,800
(Xiao Jue, styled Huaijin,
General Fengyun)

82
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,840
He Rufei,

83
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:08,240
(General Feihong of Wei)

84
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,200
Huayuan is less than a hundred li
from Mingshui.

85
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,840
Why has your reinforcement
arrived so late?

86
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,600
A rope saws wood.

87
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:25,920
Water penetrates stones.

88
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:27,600
One day,

89
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,240
you two will become

90
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,080
Wei's Twin Stars.

91
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,680
With joint forces,

92
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,080
you shall wield the swords
to guard our land

93
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,440
and its people.

94
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,760
You are unworthy

95
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,960
of the Qinglang Sword
my father entrusted to you.

96
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:05,440
(Yaojing City)
General Feihong's returned triumphantly!

97
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:06,720
General Feihong!

98
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,240
Welcome, General Feihong!

99
00:06:09,310 --> 00:06:19,260
(General Feihong's Mansion)

100
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:45,440
Young Master,

101
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,200
the Master awaits you in his study.

102
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,520
Ermao.

103
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:03,960
Madam,

104
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,320
now that you're here,

105
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,520
visit the Young Lady.

106
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:08,480
Watch your tongue.

107
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,720
There is only the Young Master.

108
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,320
The Young Lady...

109
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:14,940
(Tang Jia, He Yan's mother)

110
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,400
She's recuperating at Yuhua Temple.

111
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:35,780
Sit.

112
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,680
Yan,

113
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,480
you've been away for years,

114
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:46,480
(He Yuansheng, He Yan's father)
enduring military hardships.

115
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,800
It must have been hard.

116
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:50,440
Father,

117
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:51,720
it's not hard at all.

118
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,480
Honoring our family

119
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,680
fills me with joy.

120
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,290
Yan,

121
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:58,960
I'm glad you're home.

122
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,480
For a young lady,

123
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,560
to wield weapons

124
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:02,880
is improper.

125
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:04,160
Honoring the family

126
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,000
should be men's duty.

127
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:08,760
Now that you're back,

128
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,760
it's time to embrace your true identity

129
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,680
as a woman.

130
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,080
About our family's title,

131
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,400
you don't need to worry.

132
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,320
I have a solution.

133
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,480
A solution?

134
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,240
What solution?

135
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,360
You've sacrificed

136
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,520
for our family for years.

137
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:23,880
It's been tough for you.

138
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,760
From now on,

139
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,480
let me handle these matters.

140
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,159
This is

141
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,760
your brother you never met,

142
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:36,520
(He Rufei, He Yan's elder brother)
He Rufei.

143
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:37,919
When you came

144
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,320
with your mother at three,

145
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,600
due to his congenital frailty,

146
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,880
he had been recuperating
at Yuhua Temple.

147
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,320
That's why you had to replace him.

148
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:46,760
Now

149
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:48,280
your brother has fully recovered

150
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,160
and returned.

151
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,920
Both of you

152
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,680
should return to your proper places.

153
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:53,920
Our family's act

154
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,560
of replacing a son

155
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,400
with a daughter

156
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:58,320
can then be quietly erased.

157
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:02,960
Father,

158
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,480
is this your solution?

159
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,040
Yan,

160
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,120
you must consider
our family's interests.

161
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,240
Our family

162
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,480
is a pillar of Confucian academia

163
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:17,760
and a leader in literary.

164
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,800
Now, abandoning culture
for martial pursuits,

165
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:21,880
- we...
- Father.

166
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,520
It was precisely to not disappoint you

167
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:25,680
and to guard

168
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:26,720
our family's honor

169
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:29,280
that I strove to achieve military glory.

170
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,680
I hoped that one day

171
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:33,040
I'd become a hero
like General Xiao Zhongwu.

172
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,840
You wished to emulate Xiao Zhongwu?

173
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,960
Xiao Zhongwu was a traitor to Wei.

174
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,360
It was all due to his reckless ambition

175
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,760
and warmongering.

176
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:44,760
Soldiers wield swords

177
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,280
to guard the land

178
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:47,960
and its people.

179
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:50,400
General Xiao taught me those words.

180
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,280
I refuse to believe

181
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:54,680
he was a warmonger.

182
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,800
Tomorrow, I'll attend court

183
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,200
and demand justice for General Xiao.

184
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,680
Even at the cost of my military honors,

185
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,240
I won't hesitate.

186
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,360
(Wei's Imperial Palace)
(In Mingshui Battle,)

187
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:16,200
(Wei lost over 30,000 soldiers.)

188
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:19,520
Commander Xiao Zhongwu
bears full responsibility.

189
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:23,320
(Emperor Chengping of Wei)
The Xiaos shall bury him as a commoner

190
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:26,560
and be stripped of military command

191
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,360
as punishment.

192
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,030
Your Majesty,

193
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,840
my father

194
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:36,280
was no warmonger.

195
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:37,760
Our army had

196
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:38,920
ambushes set

197
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:39,800
throughout Mingshui.

198
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:42,080
Yet on the day of battle,

199
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:43,800
the Wutuo people

200
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:46,680
somehow destroyed
all ambush points beforehand.

201
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:49,080
There must have been
a leak of intelligence.

202
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,840
I implore Your Majesty
to reopen this case

203
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,880
to clear my father's name

204
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,160
and restore justice

205
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:58,680
for Xiao Army soldiers.

206
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:01,200
By imperial decree,

207
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:06,040
summon General Feihong, He Rufei.

208
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:32,840
I, He Rufei,
pay respects to Your Majesty.

209
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:35,840
Rise.

210
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,160
Thank you.

211
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,040
General He,

212
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,320
in Mingshui Battle,

213
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,720
was there more

214
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:44,880
to Xiao Army's defeat?

215
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,600
Your Majesty,

216
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,280
there was no more story

217
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,440
to Mingshui Battle.

218
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:52,840
If not for General Xiao's

219
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,080
reckless pursuit of glory

220
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,160
and direct confrontation with Wutuo,

221
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,520
coupled with his refusal

222
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:59,280
to request aid from our Fuyue Army,

223
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:01,840
how could the battle
have turned so tragic?

224
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,760
He Rufei!

225
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:07,840
General Fengyun,

226
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,520
I tried to reason with you.

227
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,640
Yet, to absolve your father's sins,

228
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,960
you twisted the truth

229
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,400
and made baseless accusations.

230
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:16,440
I mobilized troops immediately

231
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,120
upon receiving the distress message

232
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,680
without a moment's hesitation.

233
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,240
He Rufei,

234
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:24,680
after all these years apart,

235
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:29,520
why did you become so wretched?

236
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:46,680
You dare attempt

237
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:48,280
to plead for a sinner?

238
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:49,120
You're

239
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:51,040
dragging our entire family to graves.

240
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:52,080
- Father.
- (I've meticulously imitated)

241
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,840
(your handwriting
and behavioral patterns.)

242
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:55,560
(Imitating?)

243
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:58,800
(Since you're unwilling to swap identities,
we'll talk about it later.)

244
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,640
(You've sacrificed
a lot for your brother.)

245
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:01,560
(It's been tough.)

246
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:05,360
(Let your brother express
his gratitude to you)

247
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:06,920
(and have this cup of tea.)

248
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:25,280
General Fengyun
breached court etiquette.

249
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:29,760
But His Majesty acknowledges
the Xiao family's military merits.

250
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,800
As a warning, he shall be punished

251
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,360
with 20 strokes

252
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:37,040
and kneel outside the hall till dawn

253
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,760
to reflect on his transgressions.

254
00:13:55,730 --> 00:13:58,340
(Memorial Tablet of Mother, Song Wan;
Memorial Tablet of Father, Xiao Zhongwu)

255
00:14:08,370 --> 00:14:09,860
(People's Guardian of Loyalty and Valor)

256
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:26,440
(People's Guardian of Loyalty and Valor)

257
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,480
Punishment carried out.

258
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:50,560
Your Majesty,

259
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:52,560
I admit fault.

260
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:55,640
I request to lead troops to Que City

261
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,640
to reclaim our lost territory

262
00:14:58,680 --> 00:14:59,960
and atone for my sins.

263
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:12,520
Your Majesty,

264
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:14,720
I'll sign a military pledge.

265
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:17,840
If Que City isn't reclaimed,

266
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,240
I vow never to return.

267
00:15:36,520 --> 00:15:37,840
General Fengyun,

268
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:41,440
(Xu Jingfu, Prime Minister of Wei)
His Majesty has granted your request.

269
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:46,280
Gratitude to Your Majesty.

270
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:50,400
However, Wei's soldiers

271
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:53,440
shall not be sent to futile deaths.

272
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,560
Xiao Jue,

273
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:59,200
the court won't provide any troops.

274
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:01,480
Recover the territory

275
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:04,160
through your own means.

276
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:09,360
I

277
00:16:09,880 --> 00:16:10,600
accept the decree.

278
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:13,800
Thanks, Your Majesty.

279
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:35,840
(Even if at the cost of all,)

280
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:40,480
(I will clear my father's name.)

281
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:49,570
(Several days later)

282
00:16:54,610 --> 00:16:59,010
(Yuhua Temple)

283
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:08,720
Miss.

284
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:12,480
Miss.

285
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,440
Take a walk with me by the roses.

286
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:15,740
Okay.

287
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:20,280
Be careful.

288
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:26,319
There are steps ahead.

289
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:34,560
(59, 60,)

290
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:36,360
(61...)

291
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:40,200
You're so straightforward,

292
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:42,560
unlike the delicate noble ladies

293
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:43,480
visiting the temple.

294
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,120
Yixin,

295
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,400
if I turn right

296
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:51,960
and go forward,

297
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:52,920
will it lead

298
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,120
to the rear courtyard wall?

299
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:56,640
Yes, it'll be the rear wall.

300
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:59,080
Beyond lies the hidden path I use

301
00:17:59,080 --> 00:17:59,960
to leave here.

302
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,640
Past the canyon crevice,

303
00:18:01,840 --> 00:18:03,280
it'll be beyond Yuhua Temple.

304
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:06,200
Show me around.

305
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:07,780
Okay.

306
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:17,220
(Ding Yi, He Rufei's guard)

307
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:20,280
Father showed mercy and spared her life

308
00:18:21,120 --> 00:18:22,480
due to family ties.

309
00:18:23,280 --> 00:18:25,120
But even blinded by poison,

310
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:27,480
she remains a threat.

311
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:30,080
I'll send her to Yuhua Temple first.

312
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:31,640
Watch her closely.

313
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:33,920
Spread that word

314
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:36,560
that Miss He's condition
has suddenly worsened.

315
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:39,760
Then...

316
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:43,960
I will handle it impeccably.

317
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,320
(From meditation room to bridge,)

318
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:55,640
(it takes 61 steps.)

319
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:00,680
(After the bridge)

320
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,160
(and seven more steps,)

321
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,280
(I'll reach the roses by the pond.)

322
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:06,680
(Then bypass the roses and turn right.)

323
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:15,960
(Did I miscalculate my stride today?)

324
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:18,640
(Or did I miscount?)

325
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:56,720
Who are you?

326
00:19:58,920 --> 00:19:59,600
Forgive me, miss.

327
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:00,440
I am merely

328
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,680
a devotee visiting this temple.

329
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:03,720
No offense.

330
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:07,200
Yuhua Temple's back courtyard
lies in the northwest corner.

331
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:09,280
Devotees' meditation rooms

332
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,040
are in the eastern part.

333
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:14,560
It seems you think

334
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,240
that I harbor ill intentions.

335
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:18,760
If you truly wish to die,

336
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:21,360
why care about my potential harm?

337
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:24,120
(Wishing to die?)

338
00:20:24,800 --> 00:20:25,720
Our parents gave us

339
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:26,960
our physical forms.

340
00:20:28,760 --> 00:20:30,480
One more step and you'd enter the pond.

341
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:33,040
If you disrespect life so casually

342
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,760
and disregard
your parents' nurturing grace,

343
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,280
then proceed as you will.

344
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:40,080
I won't stop you.

345
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:43,960
Nurturing grace?

346
00:20:45,120 --> 00:20:46,520
They denied me even the chance

347
00:20:46,560 --> 00:20:47,280
to speak.

348
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:49,640
They blinded me and abandoned me here.

349
00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:52,080
In that case,

350
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:54,440
my life

351
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:56,320
is now mine to command.

352
00:20:57,680 --> 00:20:58,680
In desperation,

353
00:21:00,360 --> 00:21:00,920
death

354
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:03,600
becomes easier than living.

355
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:05,800
If you're truly tough,

356
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:06,840
blindness matters not.

357
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:09,160
Even blind,

358
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:10,880
aim to be

359
00:21:12,080 --> 00:21:13,080
the most special of all.

360
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:18,720
Give me your hand.

361
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:28,160
This osmanthus candy

362
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:32,000
is the last piece left in the world.

363
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:36,000
Though inedible now,

364
00:21:37,040 --> 00:21:38,000
it remains sweet.

365
00:21:42,120 --> 00:21:42,840
I won't know

366
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:43,960
until I taste it.

367
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:48,560
Though bitter at first taste,

368
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:50,840
its core holds enduring sweetness.

369
00:21:55,360 --> 00:21:56,360
Is the moon tonight

370
00:21:58,440 --> 00:21:59,160
beautiful?

371
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:13,600
Bright moon like frost.

372
00:22:15,600 --> 00:22:16,680
Gentle breeze like water.

373
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:20,520
The serene beauty is endless.

374
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:36,920
I moved the roses

375
00:22:37,360 --> 00:22:39,680
to stage an accidental drowning

376
00:22:40,120 --> 00:22:41,440
for Young Lady at Yuhua Temple.

377
00:22:42,080 --> 00:22:42,840
But Young Lady

378
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:44,320
was pulled back by Xiao Jue

379
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,520
and avoided falling.

380
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:47,800
Why would Xiao Jue

381
00:22:47,800 --> 00:22:48,720
appear there?

382
00:22:50,240 --> 00:22:51,480
No matter who intervenes,

383
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:53,320
that woman cannot be saved.

384
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:00,440
Let her escape then

385
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,600
and die

386
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:04,680
on her way to appeal to the emperor.

387
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:20,480
(Beyond lies the hidden path I use)

388
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:21,400
(to leave here.)

389
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:24,640
(Past the canyon crevice,
it'll be beyond Yuhua Temple.)

390
00:23:57,080 --> 00:24:00,520
Young Lady, let me send you
on your final journey.

391
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:04,120
In your next life,
avoid being born a He.

392
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:51,360
Your continued existence
remains a threat

393
00:24:51,360 --> 00:24:52,320
to the He family.

394
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,080
A mere woman

395
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,920
daring to seek military glory?

396
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:58,080
Preposterous delusions!

397
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:43,260
(One month later)

398
00:26:18,280 --> 00:26:19,280
(I can see again.)

399
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:33,960
(Where am I?)

400
00:26:35,120 --> 00:26:36,240
(Didn't I die?)

401
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:54,960
With great effort,

402
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:55,520
I saved you

403
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:56,960
and restored your vision.

404
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:58,040
Why do you

405
00:26:58,080 --> 00:26:58,760
keep moving?

406
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:00,640
Master.

407
00:27:01,040 --> 00:27:03,040
(Liu Buwang, He Yan's master)

408
00:27:05,320 --> 00:27:06,840
Last I saw you so weakened

409
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:08,600
was when I rescued you

410
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:10,640
from that mountain of corpses

411
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,120
on the battlefield.

412
00:27:12,560 --> 00:27:13,240
Why ended up

413
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:14,120
like that again?

414
00:27:17,280 --> 00:27:17,960
I thought

415
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:20,240
I could survive.

416
00:27:23,320 --> 00:27:24,000
Unexpectedly,

417
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:26,560
I misjudged human nature.

418
00:27:28,400 --> 00:27:30,000
They didn't just silence me

419
00:27:32,760 --> 00:27:33,840
but sought to ensure

420
00:27:35,120 --> 00:27:36,440
I'd never speak again.

421
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:40,240
Your family

422
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:41,800
has mastered the art

423
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:43,760
of deception to perfection.

424
00:27:51,840 --> 00:27:52,400
Master,

425
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:54,760
news was scarce at Yuhua Temple.

426
00:27:55,320 --> 00:27:55,920
Do you know

427
00:27:56,120 --> 00:27:57,440
how the Xiao family fares now?

428
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:59,080
Has General Xiao's name

429
00:27:59,280 --> 00:28:00,200
been cleared?

430
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:02,640
The entire court

431
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:04,640
condemned Xiao Zhongwu.

432
00:28:05,040 --> 00:28:06,880
To stabilize the court, His Majesty

433
00:28:07,840 --> 00:28:09,080
declared him guilty soon

434
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:10,520
and almost

435
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:12,640
took away Xiao Army's
conscription rights.

436
00:28:13,360 --> 00:28:14,360
How could this happen?

437
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:16,080
Didn't His Majesty investigate?

438
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:17,600
General Fengyun,

439
00:28:18,240 --> 00:28:19,280
as fellow generals,

440
00:28:19,760 --> 00:28:21,680
I deeply respect General Xiao.

441
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:24,120
But in matters of righteousness,

442
00:28:24,360 --> 00:28:25,560
we must not speak falsely.

443
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,120
Righteousness?

444
00:28:28,600 --> 00:28:29,720
Does your righteousness

445
00:28:29,720 --> 00:28:30,920
mean delaying reinforcements

446
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,160
and letting my father,

447
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:34,720
along with 30,000 Xiao soldiers,

448
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:37,040
die in vain?

449
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:40,560
I immediately dispatched troops

450
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:42,320
upon receiving the distress call,

451
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:43,920
without any delay.

452
00:28:44,560 --> 00:28:46,640
Had I not turned the tide,

453
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,040
Wutuo's cavalry

454
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:49,480
would have reached here long ago.

455
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:54,560
As a witness, General Feihong testified

456
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:55,800
before His Majesty

457
00:28:56,360 --> 00:28:57,240
and firmly insisted

458
00:28:57,320 --> 00:28:58,520
on Xiao Zhongwu's guilt.

459
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:01,080
With such crucial witnesses present,

460
00:29:01,840 --> 00:29:02,880
they didn't look further.

461
00:29:16,240 --> 00:29:17,560
He Rufei,

462
00:29:18,360 --> 00:29:19,280
it was you

463
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:21,600
who delayed reinforcement

464
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:24,760
and caused my father

465
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:28,120
and the Xiao Army troops

466
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:29,640
to perish tragically!

467
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:32,440
Childhood classmates first,

468
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:34,120
and then

469
00:29:34,400 --> 00:29:36,000
frontier commanders.

470
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:39,640
He Rufei,

471
00:29:41,560 --> 00:29:43,000
after all these years apart,

472
00:29:45,840 --> 00:29:47,800
why did you become so wretched?

473
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:31,040
(With my mask off)

474
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:33,720
(and my ties with the He family cut,)

475
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:35,720
(from now on,)

476
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:37,680
(I am simply He Yan.)

477
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,520
(In this vast world,)

478
00:30:41,320 --> 00:30:42,960
(I'm no longer anyone's substitute.)

479
00:30:46,200 --> 00:30:48,080
(He Rufei stole my title
as General Feihong,)

480
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:50,720
(tried to kill me, and ruined my name.)

481
00:30:51,560 --> 00:30:53,160
(I won't let him off.)

482
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:58,320
(I will return to the army)

483
00:30:58,960 --> 00:30:59,960
(and honorably)

484
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:02,080
(reclaim everything that's mine.)

485
00:31:14,550 --> 00:31:19,710
(Yezhou Garrison)

486
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,000
Thank you.

487
00:32:22,150 --> 00:32:24,310
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

488
00:32:24,410 --> 00:32:28,330
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

489
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:30,450
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

490
00:32:30,540 --> 00:32:35,470
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

491
00:32:47,570 --> 00:32:48,980
♪I've seen the mountains♪

492
00:32:49,180 --> 00:32:50,590
♪And trodden through ice♪

493
00:32:50,860 --> 00:32:53,670
♪Day after day, I venture alone♪

494
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:55,370
♪Destiny is my creed♪

495
00:32:55,430 --> 00:32:56,830
♪Ideals surge beneath the surface♪

496
00:32:56,980 --> 00:32:58,770
♪Igniting the flame against the winds♪

497
00:32:59,970 --> 00:33:01,440
♪A restless yearning in my soul♪

498
00:33:01,610 --> 00:33:02,900
♪Gazing through the mire♪

499
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:05,470
♪Who cares about this boundless void♪

500
00:33:05,670 --> 00:33:07,720
♪Charge ahead with blazing fervor♪

501
00:33:08,850 --> 00:33:10,680
♪Stubbornly fighting with my life♪

502
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:15,560
♪Soaring across the world's expanse♪

503
00:33:15,650 --> 00:33:18,310
♪There must always be a longing♪

504
00:33:18,770 --> 00:33:23,830
♪Disregard the wounds to seek the light♪

505
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:26,170
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

506
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:30,130
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

507
00:33:30,370 --> 00:33:32,260
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

508
00:33:32,290 --> 00:33:36,140
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

509
00:33:36,490 --> 00:33:38,430
♪Chasing the light within my heart♪

510
00:33:38,610 --> 00:33:42,440
♪Burying frailty,
embracing life through death♪

511
00:33:42,690 --> 00:33:48,440
♪You'll meet gazes where storms brew♪

512
00:33:49,330 --> 00:33:54,800
♪With our unwavering true love,
brave the world with me♪

513
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:04,880
♪Soaring across the world's expanse♪

514
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:07,630
♪There must always be a longing♪

515
00:34:08,080 --> 00:34:13,139
♪Disregard the wounds to seek the light♪

516
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:15,489
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

517
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:19,449
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

518
00:34:19,679 --> 00:34:21,570
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

519
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:25,449
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

520
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:27,739
♪Chasing the light within my heart♪

521
00:34:27,929 --> 00:34:31,750
♪Burying frailty,
embracing life through death♪

522
00:34:32,010 --> 00:34:37,760
♪You'll meet gazes where storms brew♪

523
00:34:38,650 --> 00:34:44,110
♪With our unwavering true love,
brave the world with me♪
